data.title: Prevalence of use and acute toxicity associated with the use of NBOMe drugs
data.meta_description: There is evidence suggesting limited use of the NBOMe class of drugs as novel psychoactive substances compared with that of classical recreational drugs and other novel psychoactive substances such as mephedrone.
